The working directory will be reset when the chunk is finished running. Use the knitr root.dir option in the setup chunk to change the working directory for notebook chunks.
data = fread("hot-dog-contest-winners.csv")

# Columns: Year, Winner, DogsEaten, Country, NewRecord

Draw the plot

  1. If: “stat_count() can only have an x or y aesthetic.”, it means we need to use geom_bar(stat = “identity”). 必要时在geom_line()里写“density”。

但是！如果这是一个geom_histogram()这种只有一个变量的函数，就不能用stat，而是geom_histogram(alpha=0.4, position=“identity”)

Color

  1. Then: 填充：if the bar is lined by color (in aes(), color = NewRecord) but the entire color is still grey. use fill = NewRecord in aes().

  2. Then: if it is constant, but we want to use categorical variables use fill = factor(NewRecord) in aes().

  3. Then: different color so it goes: scale_fill_manual(“legend标题”, values = c(color, color), labels = c(“名字”, “名字”)).

  4. Then: hide the legend using scale_fill_manual(values = c(color, color), guide = “none”). Not guided!! R recommended to use “none” instead of FALSE in guide = .

axis

  1. x-axis数字分布
  • scale_x_continuous(“坐标轴名”, breaks = seq(起始, 终点, 间隔), limits = c(起始，终点))

y轴同理

标题、副标题、尾注

  • labs(title = 标题, subtitle = 副标题（用斜杠n换行）, caption = 右下角尾注)

加小字和竖线

annotate(“text”, label = “In 2001, Takeru Kobayashi gets his first win in the competition. He went on to win five more years in a row.”, x = 1995, y = 62, size = 3, family = “Georgia”, hjust = 0, lineheight = 1) + annotate(“segment”, x = 2001, y = 56, xend = 2001, yend = 50, size = 0.5)

2. Stacked Bar Chart - Obama Approval Ratings

Load the data

data$id <- seq.int(nrow(obama))

Error in nrow(obama) : object 'obama' not found

Draw the plot

Change the order in the legend

Use levels() in aes().

Change the name of the labels

Use labels = () in scale_fill_manual().

x and y axis

If x is continuous, use scale_x_discrete().

If we want to change y from 0, 0.1, 0.2…1.0 to 0%, 10%, …100%, here it goes: scale_y_continuous("", labels=scales::percent, breaks=seq(0, 1, by=0.1))

坐标轴每个标签的方向

theme(axis.test.x = element_text(angle = 45, hjust = 1), legend.position = “right”, legend.direction = “vertical”)

打印大于15%的数字作为每个bar的标签

  • geom_text(aes(label=ifelse(Percentage >=0.15, paste(sprintf(“%.0f”, Percentage*100)),"“)), position=position_stack(vjust=0.5), color=”white")

3. Trendlines in ggplot2 - Unemployment

Load the data


data = read.csv("http://datasets.flowingdata.com/unemployment-rate-1948-2010.csv", sep=",")

# Columns: Series.id, Year, Period, Value

data$Month <- as.numeric(gsub('M', '', data$Period))
data$Date <- as.yearmon(paste(data$Year, data$Month), "%Y %m")

Draw the plot

把实心点变成空心点，并且改变颜色

geom_point(color = “颜色”, shape = 1)

注意时间也是连续变量，所以用scale_x_continuous

即使我们用了breaks = seq(0,11,1)，y轴的最低点仍然不是0，所以要这样设置

  • expand_limits(y = 0)

如果想把灰色背景去掉

  • theme_light()

画线性回归的直线

用+ geom_smooth(method = “lm”, se=FALSE, color=“navy”)

**其他回归模型

平滑曲线：geom_smooth(method=“loess”, se=FALSE, span = 0.35, color=“navy”)

省略span时，它是一个degree为2的polynomial model。

更平滑的曲线，y的x二次方程：geom_smooth(method=“lm”, formula = y ~ poly(x, 2), color=“navy”)

加上模型的方程

用annotate(“label”, size=3, color=“颜色”, x = 中心点的x位置, y = 中心点的y位置, label.size=0, label = paste(“y =”,signif(reg\(coef[[1]],5 ), "+ ", signif(reg\)coef[[2]], 5), “x,”, " AdjR2 = ", signif(summary(reg)$adj.r.squared, 5))) 【背吧。】


p = 
ggplot(data, aes(x = Date, y = Value)) + 
  geom_point(color = "red", shape = 1) + 
  scale_y_continuous("Percent of Unemployed Americans", breaks = seq(0,11,1)) + 
  scale_x_continuous("", breaks = seq(1945, 2010, 5)) + 
  expand_limits(y = 0) + 
  theme_light() +
  labs(title = "US Unemployment Rate 1948-2010") + 
  geom_smooth(method = "lm")

reg <- lm(data = data, Value ~ Date)

lm = p + geom_smooth(method = "lm", se=FALSE, color="navy")

lm + annotate("label", size=3, color="dark gray", x = 1995, y = 1, label.size=0, label = paste("y = ",signif(reg$coef[[1]],5 ),"+ ",signif(reg$coef[[2]], 5),"x,", " AdjR2 = ",signif(summary(reg)$adj.r.squared, 5)))

画点图时，加文字

+ geom_text_repel(aes(label = State), size = 3) 注意别漏了repel

改变不同的region的形状和颜色

geom_point(aes(color = Home.Value, shape = region))

画某个数值的直方分布图

只用一个变量 ggplot(housing, aes(x = Home.Value))

  • geom_histogram(binwidth = 每一条的宽度, col = 线条颜色, fill = 填充色, alpha = .2)

用bar图画每个区域的平均值

两个变量 ggplot(housing.sum, aes(x = State, y = Home.Value)) + geom_bar(stat = “identity”)

用不同颜色透明度表示数值大小和分布 theme(legend.position = “top”) + geom_point(aes(color = Date), alpha = 0.5, size = 1.5, position = position_jitter(width = .25, height = 0))

按照年份设置颜色：

scale_color_continuous(name = "“, breaks = c(1976, 1994, 2013), labels = c(”76“,”94“,”13“), low =”blue“, high =”red")

5. Faceting

Draw the plot

facet：facet_wrap()把一堆堆叠的线拆成每个state一个图，ncol指定每一行多少个子图。theme_minimal()不那么重要。

如果是facet_grid()，它把每一个histogram或者line图拉开，写成(~Year)就是扁宽的十个横条，一条代表一年；写成(Year ~ .)就是高瘦的十列，一列代表一年； 如果是facet_wrap()，它把每一个图变成小方框，不是长条。

密度分布图和提琴图

Load the data

频次直方图 geom_histogram(alpha = .5)

密度图 geom_density(alpha = .5)

提琴图里的注意事项 1. 在aes()里用factor()和对应的平均数或者其他指标； 2. 在geom_violin里再写一次aes(fill = lg)； 3. 写+ geom_jitter() 把点点也都加上。

ECDF


library(ggbeeswarm)

ggplot(tophitters2001, aes(avg)) + 
  stat_ecdf(geom = "step", aes(color = lg)) + 
  scale_y_continuous("ECDF", breaks = seq(0,1,0.25)) + 
  scale_x_continuous("Batting Average") + 
  scale_color_manual("LeaGue", values = c("violet", "sky blue")) + 
  labs(title = "MLB Averages") + 
  theme_light() + 
  geom_hline(yintercept = 0.5, linetype = "dashed") + 
  geom_vline(data = subset(tophitters2001, lg == "NL"), aes(xintercept = quantile(avg)[3]), linetype = "dashed") + 
  geom_vline(data = subset(tophitters2001, lg == "AL"), aes(xintercept = quantile(avg)[3]), linetype = "dashed")
